org.biojava.nbio.structure.symmetry.gui

Class SymmetryCalc

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biojava.nbio.structure.symmetry.gui.SymmetryCalc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, AlignmentCalculationRunnable

    public class SymmetryCalc
extends Object
implements AlignmentCalculationRunnable
    Calculates a symmetry analysis and displays the results. Linked to the SymmetryGUI. Does not generalize, uses CeSymm class directly to allow for the symmetry axis recovery.
    Since:
    4.2.0
    Author:
